Google Cloud Platform (GCP) is a suite of cloud computing services providing infrastructure, platform, and serverless tools, designed for high-performance computing, data analytics, and AI/ML on Google's global infrastructure. It offers over 200 services to help businesses optimize, secure, and scale operations. 
