Key GCP Product Categories
Compute: Virtual machines (Compute Engine), serverless applications (App Engine), and container management (Kubernetes Engine).
Storage & Databases: Scalable storage (Cloud Storage) and NoSQL/Relational databases (Bigtable, Cloud SQL).
Data Analytics & AI: Big Data analytics (BigQuery) and machine learning tools (Vertex AI, TensorFlow).
Networking: Global load balancing, DNS services, and secure connections (Cloud Interconnect).
Security & Management: Cloud Security Command Center and operations tools for monitoring. 
