Key Benefits of GCP
High Performance & Security: Leverages Google's infrastructure, which is known for security and speed.
Cost Management: Flexible pricing models and automatic scaling to cut costs.
AI/ML Focus: Extensive, pre-built machine learning and AI capabilities.
Hybrid & Multi-cloud: Solutions that allow for running applications across on-premises and other clouds. 
